Coming, coming!

5
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:20,000
Hurry up!

6
00:00:20,160 --> 00:00:20,920
Senior.

7
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,400
May I ask you, boss,

8
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:25,760
did you see the arsonist?

9
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:28,000
I didn't see anyone.

10
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,240
I just got back to the teahouse.

11
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:30,200
I can testify.

12
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,560
From the time I escorted Miss Qing Dai back to the teahouse

13
00:00:32,560 --> 00:00:33,320
until I heard the gong,

14
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:34,440
it was no more than half an incense stick's time.

15
00:00:38,720 --> 00:00:39,400
This teahouse,

16
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:41,160
is someone missing?

17
00:00:41,160 --> 00:00:42,200
We need more people!

18
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:43,280
They're here!

19
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:21,600
Report, sir.

20
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,400
A black-feathered arrow was found.

21
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:25,320
Return to guard duty.

22
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:26,240
Yes, sir.

23
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:29,039
Don't worry, sister.

24
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:30,400
I'll definitely catch the Blue Ghost.

25
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,200
Don't forget our bet.

26
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:35,800
Be careful.

27
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:37,720
Where's Hong Guo?

28
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,080
Where did Hong Guo go?

29
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:41,000
You go save people.

30
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:41,800
I'll guard the treasure.

31
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,800
Bring it here.

